summary:
I am a positive & happy person, always looking for innovation and disruption on the cutting edge of technology.  As a self starter with an entrepreneurial mindset, I make you perform, grow and innovate. This makes me a trusted sparring partner to stakeholders, teams and C-level. 

I lived, worked and enjoyed myself in: London | Paris | US | Israël | Australia | now happy in Amsterdam
